entry.title: tyrannyofsoulz Channel
entry.content:
__________________________
Stop the sellout of America now!
The Security & Prosperity Partnership (SPP) of North America for the establishment of a North American Union is a hostile takeover of democracy by the leaders of the United States, Canada & Mexico in collaboration with un-elected, unaccountable corporate elite "working groups" who are integrating policies and regulations between the three nations with no public forum or congressional oversight. The ultimate goals are the elimination of our Constitutional freedoms and national sovereignty, by creating a central parliament to dictate new laws, which would effectively eliminate the USA et al.
We can't just sit around and do nothing! Find out what you can do:
www.stopthenorthamericanunion.com/WhatYouCanDoMain.html
Know how it affects you, your family, your job and your freedom: www.stopthenau.org/About_The_NAU.htm
Also, Google: stop the NAU Constitutional Violations: www.stopthenorthamericanunion.com/ConstitutionalLawyers.html
Good luck to all the good people! --tos __________________________
Age: 32
